4.1  orlp ed25519 (portable Ed25519 / ref10-style field arithmetic)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Name:        orlp/ed25519 (portable C implementation)
  Location:    compiler/seeds/crypto/ed25519/
  Used by:     compiler/seeds/runtime_ed25519_ref10_glue.from_x.c
               (std.crypto Ed25519 backend glue; temporary until full .x port)
  Copyright:   Copyright (c) 2015 Orson Peters <orsonpeters@gmail.com>
  License:     zlib License
  Full text:   compiler/seeds/crypto/ed25519/LICENSE-zlib.txt

  Upstream (historical): https://github.com/orlp/ed25519

  Alterations in Shux (plainly marked for zlib condition 2):
    - Integrated as a single translation unit via .inc includes
    - Exported symbol renames (ed25519_ref10_*, sha512 → ed25519_ref10_sha512, …)
      to avoid clashing with higher-level std.crypto APIs
    - Build/glue wrappers; algorithmic core retained from upstream

